options:
A
```js
$(this).animate(
  { top: '+=100', left: '+=100' },
  {
    duration: 600,
    complete: function () {
      $(this).animate({ top: '-=100', left: '-=100' }, 600);
    },
  },
);
```

C
```js
$(this).animate(
  { top: '=100', left: '=100' },
  {
    duration: 600,
    complete: function () {
      $(this).animate({ top: 0, left: 0 }, 600);
    },
  },
);
```

D
```js
